That meme dump posted about 36 hours ago raised $3,200 to buy model rockets for my students at Howard Middle School. Y'all are AMAZING. Pat yourselves on the back.

If you want to donate more in the form of gift cards, I'll buy larger rockets to launch for the kids, as well as try to get enough engines that they can all launch twice again like they have the last two years.

https://www.donorschoose.org/project/rocketry-for-all/9308644/?rf=link-dc-2025-05-teacher_profile-teacher_8939248&challengeid=22095163&utm_source=dc&utm_medium=page&utm_campaign=project&utm_term=teacher_8939248

I love you imgur! Here is what you can expect: A post from me sometime in August after the rockets come in. It will be here on Imgur. Throughout the 2025-2026 school year, I will make posts here to keep you advised about how our year is going. in March/April of 2026 when we get to our unit on space, my kids will build and launch their own rockets. We are going to punch holes in the sky!!!!!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pOyatGy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>March 1970. There is an episode of Star Trek my mother had not seen before on TV. She is also nine months pregnant. Shortly after the episode starts, she goes into labor. But mom LOVES Star Trek, so she toughs it out until it is over.

In the hospital after I am born, she wants to name me "Deforest"; after the actor who plays Leonard "Bones" McCoy. Thankfully Dad shut that down, so Mom picked James instead. I also did not get Tiberius as my middle name. I do love Star Trek, but I love Star Wars more. By Grabthar's Hammer.

THANK YOU IMGUR!!!!!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8aA3o7M.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is me. Note the lightsaber. It is purple. Why? Ask Samuel Jackson. Yes, I wear kilts to school. The kids love it. I am the Jedi Teacher. I love you all so much, and my kids next year have no idea what is about to hit them. Thank you, thank you, thank you. Follow me to see my posts about teaching here and for updates on our rocket building in the spring of next year.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/cFffIT4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JediTeacher]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I wanted a hunting dog...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PyewOhE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FSG1CPA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PyewOhE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ProblemQueen7]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It's not us, it's them.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NEXfycc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LTMP0KZ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NEXfycc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Frenchy128]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>pause for purrs</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XP04xPI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9j9Kwav.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/XP04xPI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[absinthemindedprofessor]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Rage against the Machine .. Straight to Jail.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JTEs3Xz</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NxEf79w.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><gu