div><span></span></div><div>More fun than it sounds like, please wear wading shoes though or you'll crack your head slipping on rock grime.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JB0cRY7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Soundscloud is nice, but please don't forget to press some actual physical copies of that EP.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vs9dGDJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fast and more fun than waiting for the government to get back to you about money they owe vs. money you owe.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o90EYw7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Save room, we're having Akira for dessert.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sdPA3K2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We're making our own series marathon, with blackjack and hookers.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wqvVLht.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>*loud fan SFX*</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1juoO63.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's kind of funny, but don't actually do this. Whippets will make literal holes in your brain - not kidding.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8Ob6B11.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Which one though? Original series, the Animated series, Next Generation, Deep Space Nine, Voyager, Enterprise, Discovery, Picard, Strange New Wolrds, or Lower Decks? So much Trek, so little time.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gzUnI7N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>"Agent 408 requests a shipment of surveillance equipment and cheeseburgers with which to honeypot Krasnov?"</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/K7Q84Xj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>*Hat Man intensifies*</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WheTvvj.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mHRBFij.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This next one is going to blow your socks clean off though.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Z0k4LDz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IBX5p8z</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[circlebreaker]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I always upvote raccoons and you should too</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/c4JzMkI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4SzxJ5z.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/c4JzMkI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[oldiebutagoodie]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sage</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EvBTbXB</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FObo56z.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>1.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/u4VDxYF.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>2.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JZRMRhH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>3.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EVEg2Nn.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>4.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/blSBCbt.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>5.

